              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28168385/" class="">再版序</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59792119/" class=" " title="John Coey">John Coey</a>
                (今天我戴了費拉的帽子)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
